node.text:
We all know “the laundry chair.” It’s sleek, it’s sophisticated, it makes you feel like the has-it-all-together lead heroine in a Nancy Meyers flick — and it’s truly impeccable at collecting clothing. Don’t worry, we are not here to break you out of your laundry chair habit…but we did tap some organizing pros to turn it into a pseudo-organizing mechanism that works for you, rather than against you. Read how at the link in our bio! 👚

(Image: @sarahecrowley)
